## Test Organization

### Setup and Teardown

```ruby
class ArticleTest < ActiveSupport::TestCase
  # Run before each test
  setup do
    @article = articles(:one)
    @user = users(:john)
  end
  
  # Run after each test
  teardown do
    # Cleanup if needed
  end
  
  test "article is valid" do
    assert @article.valid?
  end
end
```

